@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pcdkna(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.29) / wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.66)))
    tmp = (v2 + v1)
    tmp = (0.57 + 0.69)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.63)))
    v0 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v2 + 0.09 + v0 + 0.78)))
    v1 = 0.77
    data[tid] = v0
